    "causal_summary": "The framework produced templated, generic UI when asked for design work (a MagicPath sector variation that did not read as on-brand). There was no reusable, advisor-routable guidance for distinctive visual design. Anthropic publishes a strong `frontend-design` skill, but it is shaped for its own plugin ecosystem, not this repository's curated `.opencode/skills` conventions (family prefixes, house SKILL/README/reference templates, schema-2 graph metadata, catalog index, advisor SQLite graph).",
